==Description==
The '''Old Amber''' is a type of [[Fossils|Fossil]].

==Details==
When an '''Old Amber''' is placed in the [[Pokémon Day Care]], it hatches into an Aerodactyl.

==Mine Layout==
The Old Amber appears in the Underground as a 4x4 sized object.<br><br>
